profile:
Fibrenew London specializes in the repair, restoration and renewal of leather, plastics, vinyl, fabric and upholstery servicing six major markets: automotive, aviation, commercial, medical, marine and residential. Utilizing our services to repair damaged materials in your vehicle, boat, airplane, home or office offers an environmentally-friendly and cost-effective alternative to replacement.

Leather Repair, Vinyl Restoration and Plastic Renewal Services in:
London, Ontario; St. Thomas, Ontario; Strathroy, Ontario; Alymer, Ontario; Lobo Township, Ontario; West Lorne, Ontario; Lucan, Ontario; Port Stanley, Ontario; Glencoe, Ontario; Mount Brydges, Ontario; Parkhill, Ontario; Dutton, Ontario; Rodney, Ontario
